{"tid":2372103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局鼓勵市民用電子渠道收發利是","createTime":"2021-01-19T11:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T04:31:06.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9e5040e1f990c7d63293a3a697f24918801cc7","tid":2372103,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"農曆新年將至，在疫情下，香港金融管理局（金管局）鼓勵市民盡量使用電子支付方法派利是，例如利用網上或手機銀行經金管局的「轉數快」或市面上其他電子錢包，取代派實體利是。電子支付方便易用，在香港已被廣泛接受。在新春佳節，各主要銀行和電子支付營運商將會配合<span class=\"red\">提供各式各樣的推廣計劃，令以電子支付方法收發利是既方便又有趣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，且免卻前往銀行兌換新鈔，安全又環保。<br />\n另外，金管局建議需要使用現金派利是的市民，在前往銀行兌換前，<span class=\"red\">可以先查看家中是否仍有剩餘的新鈔或「迎新鈔」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/19/P2021011900567.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202101%2F19%2FP2021011900567.htm&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c46d3d94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/19/P2021011900567.htm</a>"},{"pid":"15d5b2a666645927afa9d95079abc75fccd7eb39","tid":2372103,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"我們現時新鈔的庫存量達<span class=\"red\">以往新年期間新鈔發行量的兩倍，迎新鈔更達三倍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而換鈔時間由往年約兩星期延長至三星期，由一月二十六日至二月十一日，即農曆新年前一天。因此市民毋需在開首數天趕往兌換新鈔。"},{"pid":"c6dad09cd1ff4eb02b9c5dbc2f05758a225b3c52","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"長輩到時撳多咗個零點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c53c4a97c2e89240c12968ba17d191dbcf34e60","tid":2372103,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6dad09cd1ff4eb02b9c5dbc2f05758a225b3c52","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"長輩到時撳多咗個零點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"你幫手撳<br />\n撳多2個零<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11916fd72a320d2ef934be9fb2d14da5d505e484","tid":2372103,"uid":37948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6dad09cd1ff4eb02b9c5dbc2f05758a225b3c52","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"長輩到時撳多咗個零點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"擔心下d撚樣撳少個零好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a6637ee73f4c416df9e1f4e17e8c341e252aba","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c53c4a97c2e89240c12968ba17d191dbcf34e60","tid":2372103,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6dad09cd1ff4eb02b9c5dbc2f05758a225b3c52","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"長輩到時撳多咗個零點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"你幫手撳<br />\n撳多2個零<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"初一都變初三<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695befd2d13f97acabb7b56c3e24875f2de495dd","tid":2372103,"uid":291491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁不如推廣埋電子拜山 同電子屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019a9340b8b73e0ef0aed976a063b6c5b9f2080e","tid":2372103,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"695befd2d13f97acabb7b56c3e24875f2de495dd","tid":2372103,"uid":291491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁不如推廣埋電子拜山 同電子屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰認為議員應在立法會內開會，又反問清明節是否改為網上上香。<br />\n謝偉俊支持議案，他反駁鄭松泰的說法，<span class=\"red\">指電子上香已是非常普遍，更現在更有人在網上解決性生活</span>，「有啲人話性生活都可以喺網上解決咗好多，呢個我就唔再講啦。」"},{"pid":"df7744c566caff65ec798db3078246904353df07","tid":2372103,"uid":383344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「支」付寶 辱華"},{"pid":"cbb4224d543ac699f4b1f0fe59ac928b58d6d4c6","tid":2372103,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7744c566caff65ec798db3078246904353df07","tid":2372103,"uid":383344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「支」付寶 辱華"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2608bf6b3c57609c9143811b3c818ec1b778cd","tid":2372103,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1a6637ee73f4c416df9e1f4e17e8c341e252aba","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c53c4a97c2e89240c12968ba17d191dbcf34e60","tid":2372103,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6dad09cd1ff4eb02b9c5dbc2f05758a225b3c52","tid":2372103,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"長輩到時撳多咗個零點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"你幫手撳<br />\n撳多2個零<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"初一都變初三<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"提早赤口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b3e5e55c0e60ac4956